Pogo piny Israel


1  Ka piny opogi mondo dhoot ka dhoot oyud lope, to lowo ma borne romo kilomita apar nyaka wal ni Ruoth Nyasaye. Kanyo duto nobed kama ler. 
2  Bath lowono, ma borne gi lachne mita mia ariyo gi piero abich maromre noket tenge mondo ogerie Hekalu. E alwora mar lop Hekaluno nobedie kama odong’ nono ma lachne romo mita piero ariyo gabich. 
3  Bath lowono ma borne romo kilomita apar gariyo gi nus, to lachne kilomita abich, noket tenge mondo ogerie Hekalu, ma bende iluongo ni Kama Ler Moloyo, 
4  kendo mondo jodolo matiyo ni Ruoth Nyasaye e Hekalu odagie. Utegi nobed kanyo kaachiel gi Kama Ler mogerie Hekaluno nobed mita mia ariyo gi piero abich maromre, kaachiel gi kama odong’ nono molwore ma lachne mita piero ariyo gabich.


5  To bende bath lowono komachielo ma borne bende oromo kilomita apar gariyo gi nus, kendo lachne kilomita abich, noket tenge ni jo-Lawi matiyo e Hekalu. Ginibed gi mier kuno ma gidakie. 
6  To lowo modong’ ma borne oromo kilomita apar gariyo gi nus to lachne kilomita ariyo gi nus bende nyaka ket tenge mondo ogerie dala moro maduong’. Enobed mokiewo gi lowo mowal ni Nyasayeno, kendo nobed mar jo-Israel duto.


7  Ruoth marito piny bende nyaka podne lowo, momakore gi kama owal ni Nyasaye kod lowo ma dala maduong’ nitie, koni gi koni. Yo podhochieng’, lop ruoth nochwe nyaka nam Mediterenia, to yo wuokchieng’ nogik e tong’ piny. Kamano borne moa yo podhochieng’ nobed maromre gi lowo mopog ni dhoot ka dhoot. 
8  Mano ema nobed lop ruoth marito piny Israel, mondo kik ochak othir ji, to owe bath piny koma odong’ obed mar dhout Israel.


9  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho niya, “Usetimo richo aming’a un jotend Israel. Weuru timbeu mag mecho kod mag thir muthirogo ji. To timuru mana gik makare kendo mowinjore. Bende kik uchak uriemb joga e lopgi kendo. An Ruoth Nyasaye ema awacho kamano.

Rapim makare


10  

“Nyaka ji duto ti gi rapim makare kama: 
11  Rapim miluongo ni efa, mipimogo gik machalo cham, nyaka bed maromre gi rapim miluongo ni bath, mipimogo gik maliw. To rapim miporogo rapim nyaka bed rapim miluongo ni homer.

Homer achiel nyaka bed maromre gi efa apar, kendo kod bath apar.


12  “Bende rapim mag pek gik moko nyaka chal kama: Gera piero ariyo nyaka bed maromre gi shekel achiel, kendo shekel piero auchiel nyaka bed maromre gi mina achiel.

Chike mag gik michiwo ni Nyasaye


13  “Koro chiwo ma onego uket tenge e magi: Kukayo chambu, to nyaka uket tenge achiel kuom piero auchiel mag chamugo. 
14  Mor zeituni bende nyaka uket tenge achiel kuom mia achiel muyudo kuom olemo ma yiendu onyago. Nyaka upim morno gi rapim miluongo ni kor. 
15  To bende kuom rombe mia ariyo nyaka uchiw rombo achiel. Gigo ema unukel mondo obed chiwo mitimogo misengni mag cham gi misengni miwang’o pep, kod mago mag sawo, mondo richou owenu. An Ruoth nyasaye ema agolo chik kamano.


16  “Jopinyu duto nyaka ter chiwogo ir ruoth marito piny Israel. 
17  En ema nobed kochiwo jamni mitimogo misengni mag cham kod mago miolo piny, ni oganda duto mar Israel e sewni duto, koda ka sewni mitimo ka due opor, kod mitimo ndalo Sabato. Bende en ema nobed kochiwo misengni mag golo richo kod misengni mag cham gi mago miwang’o pep kod mag sawo mondo opwodhgo richo mag jo-Israel.”

