18  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho niya, “Chieng’ mokwongo mar due mar achiel nyaka utim misango gi rwath maonge songa, mondo upwodhgo Hekalu. 
19  Jodolo nyaka kaw remo moko mag chiayo motimgo misango mar golo richo mondo owir e sirni mag dhood Hekalu, kod tunge ang’wen, mag kendo-mar-misango, kendo e sirni mag dhorangeye midonjogo e laru maiye. 
20  Nyaka utim kamano bende chieng’ due abiriyo mar dueno, mondo upwodhgo richo ng’ato ang’ata ma oketho ka ok ong’eyo, kata moketho kobothne. Mano e yo ma unumigo Hekalu sik ka ler. 
21  

Chieng’ due apar gang’wen unuchak timo sawo mar Pasaka, kendo kuom ndalo abiriyo ng’ato ka ng’ato nyaka cham makati ma ok ketie thowi. 
22  Chieng’ mokwongo mar sawo, ruoth marito piny nyak chiw rwath ka misango migologo richone owuon kaachiel gi richo mag ji mamoko duto. 
23  To odiechieng’ kodiechieng’ mar ndalo abiriyo mag sawogo, nyaka ochiw ni Ruoth Nyasaye ruedhi abiriyo kod imbe abiriyo maonge songa, ka misango miwang’o pep. Bende nyaka ochiw nywok odiecheng’ kodiechieng’ ka misango mar golo richo. 
24  Nyaka chiw debe mar cham gi lita ang’wen mag mor zeituni kuom rwath ka rwath kod im ka im motimgo misango.


25  

“Kuom Sawo Maduong’ machakore chieng’ due apar gabich, due mar abiriyo, ruoth marito piny Israel nyaka tim misengni mag golo richo gi misengni miwang’o pep pilepile kuom ndalo abiriyo, mana machalre gi mago mitimo e Sap Pasaka, kendo bende nyaka bed maromre gi mago michiwo e Sap Pasaka.”

